    "58 proposed an equation to calculate the SR for Bitcoin trading, letting N denote periods; profit i denote the profit (or loss) achieved during the i th period, where 1 ≤ i ≤ N; and p 0 and p N denote the price of Bitcoin at the start and end of the given interval (i.e., N periods), with SR determined as follows:",
    "In practice, an SR between 1 and 2 is considered good.",
    "A ratio between 2 and 3 is very good, and any result >3 is excellent.",
    "Before discussing the experimental results, it is necessary to define the two terms used in this subsection to demonstrate the effectiveness of the preprocessing DQN.",
    "(a) Proposed method In the proposed method, the Main-DQN model leverages the previously described dataset of \"Multi-level DQN\" section, consisting of a two-dimensional array with elements taken from the outputs of Trade-DQN and Predictive-DQN models."
